  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Explore the forgotten depths of the kingdom of Menegroth, the tainted lands overrun by the undead since the discovery of necromancy.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Centuries ago, a war was waged by Menegroth, the kingdom of the necromancer king Tuliph. The kingdom conquered territory and devastated the borders, but was ultimately defeated. At the end of the war, its outer borders were sealed by a great wall of bones, and its interior was overtaken by hordes of undead and necromancers.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You are a fearless adventurer who dares to challenge the cursed depths of Menegroth, facing endless waves of undead in search of fame, treasure, and the secrets of the feared necromancer generals of Menegroth.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Eternity awaits those who dare to face the darkness… Will you survive?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >First you can take a look in the Passive Skill Tree:</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3618400/extras/4529172158e0938f0a56f2955000ad14.poster.avif?t=1761260110\" width=992 height=378 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3618400/extras/4529172158e0938f0a56f2955000ad14.webm?t=1761260110\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3618400/extras/4529172158e0938f0a56f2955000ad14.mp4?t=1761260110\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >After that you can start a match and collect some coins, try to do it in the Eternal Mode to be one of the best in the LeaderBoards.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3618400/extras/21ac2a4cfe32e01d10c96558c014258b.poster.avif?t=1761260110\" width=992 height=378 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3618400/extras/21ac2a4cfe32e01d10c96558c014258b.webm?t=1761260110\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3618400/extras/21ac2a4cfe32e01d10c96558c014258b.mp4?t=1761260110\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Evolve with the Skill cards in Game, it will increase your power inside of the game</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3618400/extras/3e8f274b6d86c7f73a828caa409ee618.poster.avif?t=1761260110\" width=993 height=378 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3618400/extras/3e8f274b6d86c7f73a828caa409ee618.webm?t=1761260110\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >When you be defeated go to the passives and buy some skills using the collected coins</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3618400/extras/4887da7759c09d48f54f91f218ee81e6.poster.avif?t=1761260110\" width=992 height=468 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3618400/extras/4887da7759c09d48f54f91f218ee81e6.webm?t=1761260110\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3618400/extras/4887da7759c09d48f54f91f218ee81e6.mp4?t=1761260110\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >And go again to be the better one!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3618400/extras/6b0de18f36414edb0e21c67e3b79798f.poster.avif?t=1761260110\" width=993 height=469 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3618400/extras/6b0de18f36414edb0e21c67e3b79798f.webm?t=1761260110\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >But don't forget to wath the LeaderBoard to see who are the 100 first guys, and see how mutch you need to be the King of Eternal Survival!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3618400/extras/f884818a11592ac596f3c987654e16c0.poster.avif?t=1761260110\" width=992 height=378 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3618400/extras/f884818a11592ac596f3c987654e16c0.webm?t=1761260110\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3618400/extras/f884818a11592ac596f3c987654e16c0.mp4?t=1761260110\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Explore the forgotten depths of the kingdom of Menegroth, the tainted lands overrun by the undead since the discovery of necromancy.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Centuries ago, a war was waged by Menegroth, the kingdom of the necromancer king Tuliph. The kingdom conquered territory and devastated the borders, but was ultimately defeated. At the end of the war, its outer borders were sealed by a great wall of bones, and its interior was overtaken by hordes of undead and necromancers.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You are a fearless adventurer who dares to challenge the cursed depths of Menegroth, facing endless waves of undead in search of fame, treasure, and the secrets of the feared necromancer generals of Menegroth.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Eternity awaits those who dare to face the darkness… Will you survive?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >First you can take a look in the Passive Skill Tree:</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3618400/extras/4529172158e0938f0a56f2955000ad14.poster.avif?t=1761260110\" width=992 height=378 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3618400/extras/4529172158e0938f0a56f2955000ad14.webm?t=1761260110\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3618400/extras/4529172158e0938f0a56f2955000ad14.mp4?t=1761260110\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >After that you can start a match and collect some coins, try to do it in the Eternal Mode to be one of the best in the LeaderBoards.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/361840