uted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3618400/extras/6b0de18f36414edb0e21c67e3b79798f.poster.avif?t=1761260110\" width=993 height=469 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3618400/extras/6b0de18f36414edb0e21c67e3b79798f.webm?t=1761260110\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >But don't forget to wath the LeaderBoard to see who are the 100 first guys, and see how mutch you need to be the King of Eternal Survival!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3618400/extras/f884818a11592ac596f3c987654e16c0.poster.avif?t=1761260110\" width=992 height=378 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3618400/extras/f884818a11592ac596f3c987654e16c0.webm?t=1761260110\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3618400/extras/f884818a11592ac596f3c987654e16c0.mp4?t=1761260110\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
